User Profile Size and Popularity Bias in Music Data. Next, in Fig. 2, we investigate if there is a correlation between the user profile size (i.e., number of distinct items/artists) and the popularity of artists in the user profile. Therefore, in Fig. 2a, we plot the number of popular artists in the user profile over the profile size As expected, we find a positive correlation (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
